<DOCHDR>
http://www.rxlist.com:80/cgi/generic/parox.htm 206.86.175.201 19970106224338 text/html 59806
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 06 Jan 1997 22:37:12 GMT
Server: BESTWWWD/1.0
MIME-version: 1.0
