<p>Dose Dependency Of Adverse Events </p>

<p>The table that follows enumerates adverse events that were more frequent
in the Nefazodone dose range of 300 to 600 mg/day than in the Nefazodone
dose range of up to 300 mg/day. This table shows only those adverse events
for which there was a statistically significant difference (p &lt; or =
0.05) in incidence between the Nefazodone dose ranges as well as a difference
between the high dose range and placebo. </p>

