<head>
   <title>Hydroxyzine - RxList Generic Information</title>
   <meta name="keywords" content="Adroxazine, Anxanil, Atarax, Atazina, Aterax,
Bobsule, Calmofilase, Cedar, Disron, E-Vista, Hiderax, Histan,
Hizin, Hydroxacen, Hyzine, Iterax, Masmoran, Multipax, Neucalm 50,
Novohydroxyzin, Orgatrax, Otarex, Paxistil, Postarax, Quiess, Rezine,
